snippet.title: Dungeons 2 | Announcement trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Dungeons 2 PlayStation®4 editon launch date announced. http://www.dungeons-game.com. The Dungeon Lord is back! The Ultimate Evil comes to console exclusivly on PS4™ this April. Build your dungeon and assemble an army of evil minions to conquesr the goody-goody human Overworld. This is the dungeon management sim you've been waiting for!
